==Notes== 
<li id="noteFoot01a" >'''[[#nbFoot01a|^A]]''' The fourteen countries are Argentina,<ref name=arg/> Australia,<ref name=aus/> Austria,<ref name=aut/> Belgium,<ref name=bel/> Canada,<ref name=can/> Finland,<ref name=fin/> France,<ref name=FRA/> Germany,<ref name="musikindustrie.de"/> Hungary,<ref name=hun/> Ireland,<ref name=ire/> New Zealand,<ref name=nz/> Sweden,<ref name=swe/> Switzerland,<ref name=swi/> and United States.<ref name=RIAA/></ol>
<li id="noteFoot02a" >'''[[#nbFoot02a|^B]]''' The four countries are Denmark,<ref name=den/> Poland,<ref name=pol/> Spain,<ref name=spa/> and United Kingdom.<ref name=BPI/></ol>
<li id="noteFoot03a" >'''[[#nbFoot03a|^C]]''' The four countries are Brazil,<ref name=bra/> Greece,<ref name=gre/> Italy,<ref name=ita/> and Portugal.<ref name=apf/></ol>

